      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Mediator Design Pattern -",
      "fontSize": 47.122807017543856,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Mediator Design Pattern -",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "MEQ3N33GWVA8_x_zC3coK",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 307.18899569508176,
      "y": -384.7330793483733,
      "width": 980.079345703125,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a5",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 440619425,
      "version": 465,
      "versionNonce": 1984401180,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781808152036,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Defines an Object That Encaptulation how a set of objects interact, and promote loose coupling by\npreventing them from referring to each other",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Defines an Object That Encaptulation how a set of objects interact, and promote loose coupling by\npreventing them from referring to each other",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "yDtXedZS6T7MgFpTfULt6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 322.32678024490133,
      "y": -209.6673417524857,
      "width": 1136.999267578125,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a7",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1461895297,
      "version": 1002,
      "versionNonce": 1618279964,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781788918446,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Simple we need to make a chat room, multiple users will message each other, now in one user lets say user1 has\ncontact of user2, user3, etc.. all the users contact or connections or follow!!! Now, lets say to do this we need to \nkeep an reference of all the user2, user3, user4 ka reference in the user1. Whole system gets Tightly-Coupled\nThis is wrong this is bad as it's: \n- not scalable for high number of nodes, waste resources like space and uses duplication\n- managing changes in connection will be a hellhole, as it will require change in connection reference of all nodes",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Simple we need to make a chat room, multiple users will message each other, now in one user lets say user1 has\ncontact of user2, user3, etc.. all the users contact or connections or follow!!! Now, lets say to do this we need to \nkeep an reference of all the user2, user3, user4 ka reference in the user1. Whole system gets Tightly-Coupled\nThis is wrong this is bad as it's: \n- not scalable for high number of nodes, waste resources like space and uses duplication\n- managing changes in connection will be a hellhole, as it will require change in connection reference of all nodes",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Ukqpta7QMeqgedJbf40Sz",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 278.8605285321596,
      "y": 926.33383291739,
      "width": 1043.999267578125,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1928586977,
      "version": 456,
      "versionNonce": 941113244,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781808408549,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "so for that simple keep the, medator class ki entralized class that keeps instace of everything user just n\nhave to send to mediator. mediator will pass it to the what ever user2 , the message user1 want to send \nsimple!!! ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "so for that simple keep the, medator class ki entralized class that keeps instace of everything user just n\nhave to send to mediator. mediator will pass it to the what ever user2 , the message user1 want to send \nsimple!!! ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "4Vsw-qebBIA0pJ3QwxEU4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 299.51898061634955,
      "y": 1012.8345942506548,
      "width": 1139.9991455078125,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a9",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1183964385,
      "version": 395,
      "versionNonce": 1252387868,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781808408549,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Every User will only know the mediator and this mediator will know every user, so everything is now Loosely-Coupled. \nBus utna hi simple \n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Every User will only know the mediator and this mediator will know every user, so everything is now Loosely-Coupled. \nBus utna hi simple \n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
