      "updated": 1781808722548,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "User",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "User",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "mfJPqZ-jj7h046-yfsZpm",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 338.05121045296175,
      "y": 411.3256751866752,
      "width": 214.19985961914062,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffc9c9",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "MZDOL4FYlclkt3wvt_1E5"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b15",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1331485596,
      "version": 586,
      "versionNonce": 2076578588,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1781808722548,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "vector<User> users;\nstring name;\nsendAll(msg);\nsend(msg, to);\nreceive(msg);\nmute(User);\nvector<User> muted;\nvector<User> blocked;",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "vector<User> users;\nstring name;\nsendAll(msg);\nsend(msg, to);\nreceive(msg);\nmute(User);\nvector<User> muted;\nvector<User> blocked;",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0s4aqXtFFtn9lQzB8jQGX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 599.4516459083325,
      "y": 430.00956325026743,
      "width": 497.1396179199219,
      "height": 150,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 70,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b16",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 733655076,
      "version": 279,
      "versionNonce": 112921884,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781808795003,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Without Observer pattern each instance of Users \nwill have it's list of connection which is Inefficient.\n\nAnd also we will need to store separate list of \nMuted & Blocked users for each User; \nbasically maintaining everything at User level",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Without Observer pattern each instance of Users \nwill have it's list of connection which is Inefficient.\n\nAnd also we will need to store separate list of \nMuted & Blocked users for each User; \nbasically maintaining everything at User level",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "1TyY3ouD50xNIBDnHN173",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 392.31740617893854,
      "y": 2163.753303709301,
      "width": 1258.2191162109375,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1971c2",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 70,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b17",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1803732124,
      "version": 273,
      "versionNonce": 1521282084,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "Hv9e2z6XyXfV0k3YFmMP4",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1781811543242,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Now, suppose in future, we also want to extend support for: Blocked & Muted users, \nthen we can simply add another vector<pair<Colleague,Colleague>> combination for Blocked-by(WHO) and Blocked(WHOM) account.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Now, suppose in future, we also want to extend support for: Blocked & Muted users, \nthen we can simply add another vector<pair<Colleague,Colleague>> combination for Blocked-by(WHO) and Blocked(WHOM) account.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
